Pre-Game Insights: Germany are beginning something of a new era and it will be interesting to see how much the handbrake remains off for Julian Nagelsmann’s Germans.
Jamal Musiala and Florian Wirtz remain the stars of a tricky attack.
Hungary didn’t find their best in the summer but can hurt teams and did have chances in their game against the Germans.
Germany should well win but it should be quite an entertaining match for the neutral.
